name: Remember KitKat
description: A beloved 9-year-old tabby cat, cherished mascot of Randa's Market, and the heart of the Mission District. KitKat was more than just a bodega catâ€”he was our neighborhood ambassador, our security guard, and everyone's best friend. On October 28, 2025, KitKat's life was tragically cut short when he was allegedly struck by a Waymo autonomous vehicle. The community is heartbroken. This token honors his memory and demands justice for all innocent lives.
